---
title: Easy Peasy Bulgogi-Gochujang Chicken with Jasmine Rice and Sesame Seeds
description: Super speedy, this Easy Peasy Bulgogi-Gochujang Chicken takes only 15 minutes to make. The popular Korean condiment gochujang contains chillies, fermented soybeans and glutinous rice which give it its savoury-sweet flavour, while bulgogi contains black bean puree, brown sugar and pear puree for a sweet and smoky flavour.
HIGH PROTEIN - Protein contributes to the maintenance of muscle mass.
